  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 24 Creation Points</p><p>Drain: 20 CCD Chakra</p><p></p><p>As an action, You can force all living creatures within 60ft, including yourself, to make a Constitution check, DC 15. </p><p>On a Fail they lose 8d12 Chakra and your CCD absorbs half of the rolled amount (This is not per creature). </p><p>If they do not have enough chakra to pay the cost they lose HP instead. </p><p>You can do this once per Long rest.</p>",
